definitions.definition: A morphism p such that for any other pair of morphisms f and g , if f ∘ p = g ∘ p {\displaystyle f\circ p=g\circ p} , then f = g .

main_definition: ( category theory ) A morphism p such that for any other pair of morphisms f and g , if f ∘ p = g ∘ p {\displaystyle f\circ p=g\circ p} , then f = g .
